divs: Sighting DetailsI looked out the 7th floor door from work and saw a star like object moving east to west.It was low in the sky to the north.I noticed it was roughly the same brightness as the star Vega and then realized that it had no strobe or green-red marker lights!I said to myself what the hell is that?Then watched untill it went behind some clouds.I have seen the space station and shuttel many times and this was more of a greenish color where the others are bright white.
Summary: a star like object moving east to west
